			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Here is the new Top 10 list for mages with comments from the SOE devs.  The list was kind of a cut-n-paste from Anduran's last post because the information was due about the time I became Correspondent.  =p
<br />

<br />
I'll forwarn you, there are a lot of "currently being discussed" and "class re-envision process" remarks on this list.  I'm going to try to really find out what / when this class re-envisioning will take place so we can really try to put some solid dates on the items.
<br />

<br />
Now, what I'd like to see from the mage community is this:  Feedback about the list.  What belongs, what doesn't.  Any new items to be added?  Any old items to be removed?
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">I really want constructive feedback.  If you want to complain about SOE and the list, please take it to rants.</span>  If you have constructive feedback about the ranking, content or anything else about the top 10 list.. by all means, post away.
<br />

<br />
1.Pet Upgrades - <span style="color: red">Currently being evaluated</span>
<br />

<br />

<br />
The poor scalability of our pets throughout the expansions.
<br />

<br />
A. Improve overall pet DPS -<span style="color: red"> DPS for all classes (and pets)  to be evaluated with the class Re-Envision process</span>
<br />

<br />
B. Improver overall pet defense / survivability 
<br />

<br />
 
<br />

<br />
2.Pet Focus Availability - <span style="color: red">Currently being discussed</span>
<br />

<br />

<br />
Lack of available pet focus upgrades past Diamond Prism of Companionship (casual) or Jennu's Sandals of Creation (raider).
<br />

<br />

<br />
A. Non-raiding mage:
<br />

<br />
a. Add a DoN augment.Minion of Darkness, 285 shards.
<br />

<br />
b. Omens crafted augment.
<br />

<br />
c. Better selection of drops (such as in a OoW single group trial).
<br />

<br />
d. Some type of progression quest.
<br />

<br />
B. Raiding mage:
<br />

<br />
a. Add servant of chaos to Anguish drops, such as OoW tier 2 boots.
<br />

<br />
 
<br />

<br />
3.Pet Focus Scaling - <span style="color: red">Currently being discussed</span>
<br />

<br />
Improve the way that the pet focus effects work on level 66+ pets, since the improvement they give has been largely diminished from what they did on the 61-65 pets.
<br />

<br />
4.Pet Heals and Buffs - <span style="color: red">Currently being evaluated</span>
<br />

<br />
Better buffs and heals are needed to help a mage keep their pets alive as mob power continues to increase.
<br />

<br />
A. Heals.Improve our existing line of heals
<br />

<br />
a. Fast cast, fast heal
<br />

<br />
b. Slow cast, large heal
<br />

<br />
c. Heal over time
<br />

<br />
B. Buffs.Add a Protection of Vie line of spells to help with the defensive situation and improve solo-ability / survivability.
<br />

<br />
C. Heal Crits.Give mages a chance to perform a critical heal based on nuke crit rate or AA.
<br />

<br />
  
<br />

<br />
5.Update Rains - <span style="color: red">Currently being discussed</span>
<br />

<br />
Remove the innate resists on Rains and retune the mana cost to be more in line with their corresponding DDs.Also consider allowing improved damage foci to affect rains.
<br />

<br />
  
<br />

<br />
6.Omens Spells - <span style="color: red">Currently being discussed.  Some of these issues may be evaluated as part of the class Re-Envision process.</span>
<br />

<br />
Upgrade Omens spells to be more balanced in terms of damage : mana.
<br />

<br />

<br />
A. Star Strike.2350 dmg, 485 mana
<br />

<br />
B. Blade Strike.2050 dmg, 455 mana
<br />

<br />
C. Ancient:Nova Strike.2850 dmg, 530 mana
<br />

<br />
D. Circle of Fireskin and Fireskin.Increase the the FR component from 45 to 55-62.
<br />

<br />
  
<br />

<br />
7.Pet Item summons - <span style="color: red">Currently being discussed.</span>
<br />

<br />
A. Belt should have 750hp AND worn haste.
<br />

<br />
B. Omens and PoP proc upgrades:stun, lifetap and / or rune
<br />

<br />
  
<br />

<br />
8.Fire Pet - <span style="color: red">Currently being discussed.</span>
<br />

<br />

<br />
Currently many ideas on how to make this pet useful listed on the magetower.
<br />

<br />

<br />
A. Fire has weak melee and weak defense.Pet roots self and starts chain nuking a chromatic -50 DD at the mob until mob dies, runs out of mana, or pet dies.DPS should be greater than air pet, but less than water pet.Damage scales with level of pet focus.
<br />

<br />
B. Upgraded version of our pre-50 level fire pets.Weak offense and defense, but a large self damage shield that stacks with existing mage DS.
<br />

<br />
C. Lesser version of air pet but with some unique group feature such as:bard song (+ mana regen, + hp regen or nuke boosting song), cleric ward, buff that adds procs to melees.
<br />

<br />

<br />
9. CotH utility - <span style="color: red">Currently being discussed.  This will most likely be considered as part of the class Re-Envision process.</span>
<br />

<br />
A. Make CotH available in all corpse summoning, druid 0% zones.
<br />

<br />
B. Create a cross-zone CotH ability.
<br />

<br />
C. Create an "elemental pact" style AA that negates the need for stacks of pearls.
<br />

<br />
D. Allow CotH to work on anyone within a raid.
<br />

<br />
E. Add an instant CotH AA with appropriate reuse timer.
<br />

<br />
  
<br />

<br />
10.Bugged, Broken, and Useless
<br />

<br />
A. Buffs cannot be removed from pets to deal with stacking issues. <span style="color: red">Currently being discussed for all pet classes.</span>
<br />

<br />
B. Allow Mod rods (3 charge and 1 charge version) to be used in potion belt. <span style="color: red">Currently being discussed.</span>
<br />

<br />
C. Add the nifty graphic to Mod rods as a visual cue as to when the reuse timer is up. <span style="color: red">Currently being discussed.</span><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=653282" target=_blank>Casala</a>
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1023548" target=_blank>Aderyn</a>
<br />
<a href="http://www.hneguild.com" target=_blank>Heaven and Earth</a>, Saryrn
<br />
SOE Magician Class Correspondent</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
