Currently it is:
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Level 60 - Monster Summoning III</span>
<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">Pet Level    Damage      HP     Spell     Damage Regeneration</span> 
<br />
    48              60        3300      49               30 HP/tic 
<br />

<br />
I would maybe like to see it scale with both Summoner's Boon and Minion of Darkness foci to make it something like:
<br />

<br />
       Type              Pet Level    Damage      HP     Spell     Damage Regeneration
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Unfocused</span>  48              60        3300      49               30 HP/tic
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Summoner's Boon</span>  49  65-70  3700   60  270Hp/tic
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Minion of Darkness</span>  50 68-72  4000   65  270/Hp/tic
<br />

<br />
This will give the Ms3 an actual use time by us loob mages that dont have the epic
<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">___________________________________________________________</span>
<br />
Also I have noticed that every top ten i have seen has pet durability as a major issue. maybe asking to adjust  mage AA's that effect pet HP's/regen may be a better way to ask for an upgrade over asking for a base upgrade. I was thinking of them adjusting Elemental Durability to be like:
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">Elemental Durability</span>
<br />
Category: Pet Defense/Pet Statistical
<br />
Requirements: Level 65
<br />
2 / 4 / 8 / 20
<br />
Increases Magician pet HP by 2%, 5%, 10% and 25% above the base.
<br />

<br />
This will essentially give us an extra 15% to top end pet HP's for 10 more aa's. Have them hand out refunds of 8aa's for level 3's adjustment and give the ubers an option to get the next level.
<br />

<br />
I have also noticed dps, HP, mitigration AA's but what about a Pet regen AA? Maybe something like:
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">Elemental Regrowth</span>
<br />
Category: Pet Defense/Pet Statistical
<br />
Requirements: Level 65
<br />
4 / 8 / 12
<br />
Increases Magician pet Regen by 10%, 20%, and 50% above the base. 
<br />

<br />
making unfocused high end pets able to naturally regen between 360Hp/tic and 540 Hp/tic
<br />

<br />
An uber mage with these 2 AA's maxed out, epic 2.0 and equipped with mage toys would have a MoDiscord CoW pet look something like:
<br />
