I was thinking about this today and pondered on the idea of a quested pet focus <span style="font-weight: bold">augment</span> / item. I thought that it would be pretty awesome to maybe have a new quest added onto the Temple of Solusek Ro quest. Something along the lines of combining the shovel, torch, broom and stein into a new all around low Focus for 4 to 49 pets but then being able to quest and get it slowly upgraded in power, maybe up to the Minion of Eternity focus or higher. Possibly even maxing out at chaos level or have a cool right clicky for our pet on it...burnout, a DS, velocity, summon companion, shrink, etc. It would not only give us mages a fun alternative to raids and missions but give us a new option for upgradeability.
