				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Root isn't that great of a solo tool; snare is better. It's more crowd control than anything IMO.
<br />

<br />
If we want to solo better we should probably request better heals. Increase Renewal of Jerikor to a 2500-3000ish heal, increase mana cost a bit, keep the casting time, remove the recast time. That would allow us to pretty much sustain a pet forever, but would be mana intensive at the same time.
<br />

<br />
One thing that needs to be done IMO, change all nukes to conjuration, we are summoners for gods sake, not wizard's.
<br />

<br />
Also, do something to make mage pets the obvious kings of the pet world. It doesn't have to be through DPS (though it is preferred), just do something. Pets are supposed to the center of our power, make that clear to everyone.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=490410&resize=true" target="_blank" class="postlink">Dalren Fieryblade, Invictus Verite (Updated 1/28/05)</a>
